}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== :This hub identifies as two 0409:005a devices to the host system.
"K-7PORT-1-N114-R0", "JARGY CO., LTD.", and a lead-free logo is silkscreened on the main board.
"K-4PORT-2-R0", "JARGY CO., LTD." is silkscreened on the stand-alone USB port board. :[http://www.jargy.com.tw/ Jargy] manufactures USB hubs, and is certainly the manufacturer of this one.
The power adapter included with the hub may have been a '''Sunny''' SYS1308-1505-W2.
